# ENTITY::SET_ENTITY_CANT_CAUSE_COLLISION_DAMAGED_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity
* **ENTITY_INDEX** damagingEntity

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Sets an entity to not have collision damage from the other entity
